page.title: 01Gazetteer
page.content: Tregadillet-Tregadillet is a village which is only partially within our rectangle. Langore-Langore is the largest complete settlement in our area.Its total population is 114. Truscott-Truscott is a small settlement consisting of twelve dwellings. Farms-The farms in our area are:Kestle Farm,Athill Farm,Atway Farm,Lower Truscott Farm,Hendragreen Farm,Newchurches Farm,Kernick Farm,Rings Farm,Beechcroft Farm,Trevallett Farm,Tankers Lake and Newhouse Farm. Woods-The woods in our area are: Hendragreen Wood,Trevallett Wood,Rings Wood,Cannapark Wood,Athill Wood, Trebursey Wood and most of Castle Hill Plantation. Major Amenity-A 90 acre golf course.
